%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.19/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Python SDK
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS
    participant REST as REST Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: REST API Request (Model Registration)
    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP/8080
    Istio->>REST: Forward (mTLS enforced)<br/>AuthorizationPolicy
    REST->>MLMD: PutContextType / PutContexts<br/>gRPC/9090 plaintext (localhost)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT metadata<br/>username/password auth
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>REST: gRPC Response
    REST-->>Istio: HTTP 201 Created<br/>JSON Response
    Istio-->>Client: Response (mTLS)

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: UI User Interaction

    participant Browser as Browser
    participant UIBFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Browser->>UIBFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry/:id/registered_models<br/>kubeflow-userid header
    UIBFF->>K8s: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>UIBFF: Allowed
    UIBFF->>REST: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
    REST->>MLMD: GetContexts<br/>gRPC/9090 plaintext
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT metadata
    DB-->>MLMD: Results
    MLMD-->>REST: gRPC Response
    REST-->>UIBFF: JSON Response
    UIBFF-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: KServe Model Download (CSI)

    participant KServe as KServe Init Container
    participant CSIInit as mr-storage-initializer
    participant Storage as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    KServe->>CSIInit: model-registry:// URI
    CSIInit->>REST: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/model_artifacts/{id}<br/>HTTP/8080
    REST->>MLMD: GetArtifacts<br/>gRPC/9090
    MLMD-->>REST: Artifact with storage URI
    REST-->>CSIInit: ModelArtifact JSON (storage location)
    CSIInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Storage credentials
    Storage-->>CSIInit: Model files
    CSIInit-->>KServe: Model ready at local path
